==Vietnamese==

===Etymology===
From [[阮朝]] ([[Nguyễn triều]]) is the [[Sino-Vietnamese]] form of the name; the purely Vietnamese form of the name is [[Nhà Nguyễn]].

===Proper noun===
{{vi-proper noun|Nguyễn triều|sc=Hani}}

# [[Nguyen Dynasty]], a dynasty of Vietnam (1802-1945)
